                    <ul class="mt-8 space-y-2 text-slate-600">
                        <li><strong>Technical Challenges:</strong> Generative AI, wisdom graphs, real-time personalization, latest UX.</li>
                        <li>Founder-level equity and ownership opportunities for those shaping the core product and vision.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="mt-10">
                        <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Apply as Developer</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-slate-900 text-white">
